       fhir:comment [ fhir:v "* Introduced search of non errored(valid) records using ':not' modifier, a validation message will be provided if user tries to search using any other status or a list of statuses, only supported status is 'entered-in-error'.\n* Entered-in-error-No other change to be incorporated apart from the status & the mandatory behaviour.\n* The update operation to entered-in-error status of Appointment shall throw error if the following Appointment has CarePlan links. \n* For update operation-All other changes in the payload apart from the status change shall be neglected if the status is entered-in-error." ] ;
